mxCell.value: Alerts for all nodes are sent by Netdata cloud

Netdata agent(s)
- Installed on remote Linux node(s)
- Scrape each Windows node every few sec
- Connected to the cloud for infrastructure monitoring at scale
- Retention limited only by available RAM
- Possibility for high availability via replication/streaming

Windows Exporter (Prometheus) on each node
- Exposes system and application data
- Has minimal footprint
- FOSS, supported by a vibrant community

- Real-time dashboards with long history
- Advanced grouping and filtering
- Advanced role based access
- Anomaly detection
- Custom dashboards
- Event feed
